title: Various Artists - Caferino Albuquerque Vol. 5 [trip-hop]
description:
Caferino Albuquerque vol. 5, like always, with good chunks of undiscovered treasures of trip-hop, this time with a slight theme. Autumn has come in our hearts, so most of these songs are quite melancholic.
Enjoy!

tracklisting:
1. Ilya - "Bellissimo" (5:02)
2. Slouch - "Parachute Dub" (4:57)
3. Bergman - "Like a Game" (3:40)
4. Leaf - "Intelligent Design" (5:35)
5. Sunday Munich - "Dizzy" (3:42)
6. Antenne - "Blue Light" (6:23)
7. Krom - "Watching Over You" (5:53)
8. Pelican City - "Sesame Street" (5:08) (yup, it&#039;s Danger Mouse)
9. Jute - "Opium" (9:09)

P.S. And yes, Dizzy is a poor radiorip, but do you have another rip? Come on, still I&#039;m not a magician to be able to find the rarest thing you can imagine.
